<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="transform-vt">transform <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /træns'fɔːm/    美 /træns'fɔːm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使改变；使变形；使改观</strong></h4>
<p>to completely change sth / sb, especially in a way that improves it or them：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Water can <strong>transform</strong> a desert <strong>into</strong> a garden. 
水能使沙漠变为花园。</p></div></div>